summary: An Ordinance appropriating the sum of Seven Thousand Six Hundred Forty-nine and 03/100 Dollars ($7649.03) from the General Fund of the City of Seattle, in accordance with the provisions of Ordinance Number 13513, on account of the cost and expense of the improvement of Third Avenue et al, by regrading the same, as authorized by Ordinance Number 14993, creating Local Improvement District No. 1345.
